<section class="text">
<p>I like Hori products and use at least three with my Switch (the Taiko drum, plus pad left joy con thing, and this split pad). I use my Machina split pad almost all the time when my Switch is undocked. It feels great, has regular pro controller amount of travel on the joy sticks, has a pretty great plus pad, and has turbo. It also has a programmable button on the bottom, but I don't really use it much. I like the blue one and the PacMan one, but I'm not going to bother selling mine to get the color/design I prefer.</p></section>
