<section class="text">
<p><a href="https://www.nintendolife.com/users/The-Chosen-one" class="mention" data-username="The-Chosen-one" rel="nofollow">@The-Chosen-one</a> D pad is great, it's a little bigger than the pro and I like that. For FPS this is amazing. I play Bulletstorm all the time in handheld mode, whereas with joy-con i never did.</p></section>
